🔍 SQL Skills Demonstrated
•	🧠 Advanced JOINs (multi-table analysis)
•	📊 Window Functions (RANK, NTILE, ROW_NUMBER)
•	🔁 CTEs & Subqueries
•	📈 KPI Calculations
•	📉 Trend Analysis
________________________________________
🧪 Sample Query
SELECT 
    CustomerID,
    SUM(TotalAmount) AS Revenue,
    RANK() OVER (ORDER BY SUM(TotalAmount) DESC) AS Rank
FROM Sales_Orders
GROUP BY CustomerID;
